</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Input shaft
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Select countershaft 5th gear shim as follows.
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Push down bearing outer race and measure clearance between transaxle right case and bearing outer race using straightedge (1) and feeler gauge (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A521037.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "71.702mm" ver = "01" gw = "161" gh = "187"/>
</figure>
</s2>
